text: Our company uses personal information within the scope of predetermined purpose in consideration of business content and scale, and will not use it beyond the purpose.

In order to provide Web application "SKY FORCE" (hereinafter referred to as "this application") and the service related to this application (hereinafter referred to as "this service"), EQS, Inc. will request user information, and establish Web Application Privacy Policy (hereinafter referred to as "this policy") to protect the information we acquired.
